Source: python-charade
Section: python
Priority: extra
Maintainer: Oxan van Leeuwen <oxan@oxanvanleeuwen.nl>
Build-Depends: debhelper (>= 9), dh-python, python-all (>= 2.6.6-6~), python-setuptools, python3-all, python3-setuptools
Standards-Version: 3.9.5
Homepage: https://github.com/sigmavirus24/charade
Vcs-Git: https://github.com/oxan/charade-debian.git
Vcs-Browser: https://github.com/oxan/charade-debian
X-Python-Version: >= 2.7
X-Python3-Version: >= 3.2

Package: python-charade
Architecture: all
Depends: ${misc:Depends}, ${python:Depends}
Description: universal encoding detector
 Universal encoding detector for Python, which currently supports:
 .
  * ASCII, UTF-8, UTF-16 (2 variants), UTF-32 (4 variants)
  * Big5, GB2312, EUC-TW, HZ-GB-2312, ISO-2022-CN (Traditional and
    Simplified Chinese)
  * EUC-JP, SHIFT_JIS, ISO-2022-JP (Japanese)
  * EUC-KR, ISO-2022-KR (Korean)
  * KOI8-R, MacCyrillic, IBM855, IBM866, ISO-8859-5, windows-1251 (Cyrillic)
  * ISO-8859-2, windows-1250 (Hungarian)
  * ISO-8859-5, windows-1251 (Bulgarian)
  * windows-1252 (English)
  * ISO-8859-7, windows-1253 (Greek)
  * ISO-8859-8, windows-1255 (Visual and Logical Hebrew)
  * TIS-620 (Thai)
 .
 This is the Python 2 version of the package.

